subSubSection.paragraph:
Distribution. Nearctic, Neotropical (at high altitudes as far south as Costa Rica ), Oriental, and Palaearctic regions, Hawaiian Islands ( Beardsley & Huber 2000 ), Papua New Guinea , and South Africa ; one species (
O. vulgatus Haliday
) was apparently unintentionally introduced into New Zealand .
